OL,3,CNewcastle United sells St James' Park
OL,4,Cto club owners
OL,6,FNewcastle United sold St James' Park
OL,7,Fand adjacent land to another company
OL,8,Fowned by the club's shareholders last
OL,9,Fseason.
OL,11,FIt emerged as financial figures were
OL,12,Fpublished on Tuesday (31 March)
OL,13,Fcovering the 12 months to 30 June,
OL,14,F2025, during which the club ended its
OL,15,F70-year wait for a major domestic
OL,16,Ftrophy with its Carabao Cup win, but
OL,17,Falso had no European football.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
