CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1775049067
OL,3,CNewcastle United sells St James' Park
OL,4,Cto club owners
OL,6,FNo announcement has been made on plans
OL,7,Ffor a new stadium.
OL,9,FDavid Hopkinson, chief executive,
OL,10,Fsaid: "Our financial results reflect
OL,11,Fnot only strong progress on and off
OL,12,Fthe pitch, but also the firm
OL,13,Ffoundations being laid for the future
OL,14,Fwe all aspire to.
OL,16,F"Thanks to the continued backing of
OL,17,FPIF and the Reuben family, we are
OL,18,Fbetter positioned than ever to invest
OL,19,Fin our long-term vision and create the
OL,20,Fconditions for sustained success.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
